snippet: Andy Murray took special pride in reaching the world number one ranking in an era when Roger Federer, Rafa Nadal and Novak Djokovic - arguably some of the greatest players ever - have dominated the game....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray took special pride in reaching the world number one ranking in an era when Roger Federer, Rafa Nadal and Novak Djokovic - arguably some of the greatest players ever - have dominated the game.

headline.print_headline: Murray Takes Pride in Reaching No. 1 in Golden Era
headline.main: Murray Takes Pride in Reaching No. 1 in Golden Era
